544069, \"rank\": 0.0004829467125003185, \"text\": \"Haliburton\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  \\\"It's an honor to introduce the 2024 USA Basketball Men's National Team,\\\" Grant Hill, the team's managing director, said in a statement.\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.17972206729597e-25, \"text\": \"Grant Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am grateful to these 12 men for their commitment to represent USA Basketball.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999335565618196, \"rank\": 6.644785327233088e-05, \"text\": \"USA Basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States is home to some of the best basketball players in the world and I appreciate the vast interest in being part of this roster.\\\"\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999561169, \"rank\": 3.981118903299942e-11, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greatness Unites.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 USA Men's National Team is here.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9969945356294062, \"rank\": 0.0029324421061209496, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83c\\uddf8#USABMNTpic.twitter.com/I2jOLsrcQv  - USA Basketball (@usabasketball)April 17, 2024    USAB officials traveled to present the players with special Team USA Olympic jerseys.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.5783761653104485e-12, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Training camp for theOlympicsdoesn't start until July 5, in Las Vegas, and Team USA's first game is not until July 28 - but players will soon participate in content for Olympic promotion, sources close to the players said.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Valley\", \"score\": 0.9749360618892415, \"rank\": 0.02221081162307171, \"text\": \"Las Vegas\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Valley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Valley\"}, {\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.5783761653104485e-12