rd, a favorite to make the team of both Durant and James, is battling a knee injury and his status for the start of the playoffs with theLA Clippersis unknown.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2152, \"end\": 2158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1548231249288488e-20, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.059282856655365e-14, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  Davis and Adebayo, two Olympic veterans, are obvious additions, given their size and defensive prowess, while Edwards and Haliburton are two young, dynamic guards whom USA deep thinkers view as a bridge between the present and future of the American men's national team.\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2298, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.750309805505171e-14, \"text\": \"Adebayo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\"}, {\"begin\": 2410, \"end\": 2420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\", \"score\": 0.9994746892544069, \"rank\": 0.0004829467125003185, \"text\": \"Haliburton\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\"}, {\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2537, \"title\": \"http://dbped